What is the value of $\frac{14!}{5!9!}$ ?

$\frac{14!}{5!9!} = \frac{14 \times 13 \times 12 \times 11 \times 10 \times 9!}{5!9!} = \frac{14 \times 13 \times 12 \times 11 \times 10}{5 \times 4 \times 3 \times 2 \times 1} = \frac{14 \times 13 \times 12 \times 11 \times 10}{120} = \frac{240240}{120} = 2002$

Final Answer: $\boxed{2002}$
